1711
02:16:11,000 --> 02:16:17,439
<i>Some fine day</i>

1712
02:16:17,960 --> 02:16:22,750
<i>How are things in Glocca Morra?</i>

1713
02:16:23,440 --> 02:16:27,115
<i>Is that little brook</i>
<i>Still leaping there?</i>

1714
02:16:28,240 --> 02:16:31,835
<i>Does it still run down to Donny Cove</i>

1715
02:16:32,080 --> 02:16:37,473
<i>Through Killybegs,</i>
