02:17:14,520 --> 02:17:18,957
<i>And each lad</i>
<i>That comes a-whistlin'</i>

1725
02:17:19,560 --> 02:17:23,553
<i>''Too-ra-lay''</i>

1726
02:17:23,920 --> 02:17:29,790
<i>''How are things in Glocca Morra...</i>

